Using Pycharm
Advantages:
-Direct integration of version control (Git Hub)
-Ability to visualize variables
-Ability to step through and debug code


Creating a new python project and script:
https://www.jetbrains.com/help/pycharm/creating-and-running-your-first-python-project.html

Setting up version control:
1) Git download link: https://git-scm.com/download/win
2) Enabling version control for a project: https://www.jetbrains.com/help/pycharm/enabling-version-control.html
